ZH: 我今天早上吃了一片吐司。
EN: I had a slice of toast this morning.
ZH: 你喜欢什么口味的吐司？
EN: What flavor of toast do you like?
ZH: 请给我两片吐司。
EN: Please give me two slices of toast.
ZH: 吐司涂了黄油很好吃。
EN: Toast with butter is delicious.
ZH: 我通常会抹果酱在吐司上。
EN: I usually spread jam on my toast.
ZH: 这家餐厅的吐司非常香。
EN: The toast at this restaurant is very fragrant.
ZH: 吐司上撒点儿糖会更加美味。
EN: Toast sprinkled with sugar will be even more delicious.
ZH: 你喜欢蘸牛奶的吐司吗？
EN: Do you like to dip your toast in milk?
ZH: 吐司配一杯咖啡，早餐就完美了。
EN: Toast with a cup of coffee makes a perfect breakfast.
ZH: 我喜欢吃烤得金黄的吐司。
EN: I like to eat toast that is golden brown.
ZH: 我们家的吐司机器坏了。
EN: Our toaster is broken.
ZH: 你能帮我把吐司弄出来吗？
EN: Can you help me get the toast out?
ZH: 今天早上我意外地烤糊了吐司。
EN: I accidentally burned the toast this morning.
