EN: The toast at this coffee shop is made very delicately.
ZH: 吐司的热气散发出来的香味很诱人。
EN: The aroma of toast wafting in the air is very tempting.
ZH: 你可以选择多种面包作为吐司的材料。
EN: You can choose from a variety of breads as your toast base.
